### Environment Variables at Runtime

**Injected via docker-compose environment:**
| Variable | Source | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `CDS_PROJECT_NAME` | GitHub vars | Project identifier |
| `CDS_RELEASEMODE` | Workflow logic | `development` or `production` |
| `CDS_COMMIT_ID` | GitHub event | Git commit hash (used as image tag) |
| `SERVER_PORT` | Config JSON | Main exposed port |
| `PORT_API` | Config JSON | Internal API port |
| `PORT_SOCKETIO` | Config JSON | Socket.IO port |
| `PATH_SOCKETIO` | Config JSON | Socket.IO URL path |
| `LOG_LEVEL` | Workflow logic | `debug` (dev) or `warning` (prod) |
| `HOST_HOSTNAME` | Server `/etc/environment` | Host machine name |
| `CDS_DOCKER_DNS` | Server `/etc/environment` | Docker DNS server |

**React build args (baked into static build):**
| Arg | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `REACT_APP_PATH_SOCKETIO` | Socket.IO path for client connection |
| `REACT_APP_CDS_SITE_MODE` | `development` or `production` |
| `REACT_APP_PUBLIC_PROJECT_NAME` | Display name in UI |

